Interface Tag

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TagImpl

    public interface Tag
    A tag from an activity to some object.
    Author:
    The Sakai Foundation.

    • Method Detail

      • getActivityRef

        String getActivityRef()
        Returns:
        A reference for the activity from which the tag originated.

      • getObject

        Object getObject()
        Returns:
        The object to which the tag was applied.

      • getFields

        List<String> getFields()
        Method to get the displayable data for each of this tag's fields. This list should be in the same order as the columns returned by TagList.getColumns.
        Returns:
        A list of data corresponding to displayable fields for this tag.

      • getField

        String getField(TagColumn column)
        Method to get a specific field of data for this tag based on a specific column from the list returned by TagList.getColumns().
        Parameters:
        column - The TagColumn object representing the specific field of data to retrieve from this tag.
        Returns:
        The data for the field associated with the given column.
